name: Baptism Of Fire
description: Tribute to Leo Prinsloo and Lloyd Mtombeni. Leo Prinsloo is a heroic armoured truck driver who gained viral fame for keeping his cool when his armoured truck was attacked in South Africa. His partner Lloyd Mtombeni remained super calm, even though he had only been on duty for a few days. First 10 Tezos will be donated to https://www.childlinesa.org.za/
